<p style="font-family:Times New Roman"><span style="color:#00FBFF;">According to <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chico,_California" target="_blank">Wikipedia</a>, Chico is a city in Northern California with a population of over 86 thousand.</span></p>
<ul>
<h2 style="font-family:Arial"><span style="color:#00FBFF;">Quick facts:</h2>
<li style="font-family:Times New Roman"><span style="color:#00FF0F;">Home of California State University, Chico</span></li>
<li style="font-family:Times New Roman"><span style="color:#00FF0F;">Boasts USA's 24th largest city park, Bidwell Park</span></li>
<li style="font-family:Times New Roman"><span style="color:#00FF0F;">Sierra Nevada brewery founded in Chico in 1980</span></li>
</ul>
